text: Kellyville is an electoral district of New South Wales. It was created in 2023, taking in most of the abolished electorate of Baulkham Hills. It is a conservative electorate that has only ever been held by the Liberal Party. Kellyville is located in the Hills District of Sydney, which is the most conservative (Liberal-leaning) district in any Australian capital city. ==Election results== ==References== Category:2023 establishments in Australia Kellyville
